Variation. Based on six tadpoles at stages 25–37 , all from Ranomafana National Park ( ZCMV 3619, 3631) of which two are DNA voucher specimens (
Table 6
). All the specimens are deposited in the UADBA collection. TL and BL are 23–29 mm and 7–13 mm , respectively. BW 94–107 % of BH; ED 9–13 % of BL ; RN 46–83 % of NP; IND 45–61 % of IOD; SS 54–63 % of BL ; TMH 95–100 % of MTH; TMW 50–71 % of BW ; MTH 61–77 % of BH; ODW 42–79 % of BW ; LTRF 7 ( 5–7 )/ 3 .
